				<p class="italic">Angers Loire Habitat</p>
				<ul class="list-disc ml-5">
					<li>Tenant needs management</li>
					<li>Hotline for housing applicants</li>
				</ul> <br>

				<p class="font-bold">Technical and Customer Relations Advisor | June-August 2022</p>
				<p class="italic">Verisure Angers</p>
				<ul class="list-disc ml-5">
					<li>Supporting and resolving customer needs</li>
					<li>Directing customers to the right services</li>
					<li>Administrative handling of customer needs</li>
				</ul> <br><br>

				<!-- ===================================================================== -->

				<h2 class="text-center text-xl">Skills</h2>
				<p><b>OOP :</b> C++, C#, Java</p>
				<p><b>WebDev :</b> HTML/CSS, Javascript, PHP, React, Svelte, Astro</p>
				<p><b>Database :</b> SQL, PostgreSQL, Firebase</p>
				<p><b>Others :</b> Python, Git/GitHub</p>
				<br><br>

				<!-- ===================================================================== -->

				<h2 class="text-center text-xl">Formations</h2>

				<p class="font-bold mt-5">Computer Science degree | 2021 - 2024</p>
				<p>Year 1 in Mathematics-Computer Science, Year 2-3 in Computer Science</p>
				<p class="italic">Université d'Angers</p>
				<br>

				<p class="font-bold mt-5">Baccalauréat Général | 2021</p>
				<p>Specialized in Mathematics and Digital and Computer Science</p>
				<p class="italic">Institution Mongazon</p>
				<br>
			</WideBlock>
			<div class="flex flex-row ml-[25%] mr-[25%] justify-center">
				<SmallBlock title="Languages">
					<ul class="text-center">
						<li>French (native)</li>
						<li>English (bilingual)</li>
					</ul>
				</SmallBlock>
				<SmallBlock title="Passions">
					<ul class="text-center">
						<li>Worldbuilding</li>
						<li>Tabletop RPGs</li>
						<li>Video Game Development</li>
					</ul>
